      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition, appearing and performing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. With every surface gleaming and its mechanical performance flawless, it\u2019s a rare find for any driver who demands the very best.",
