    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It drives smoothly and has clearly been well-cared for over the years! If you're looking for a great car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure without breaking the bank, this is the one. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out with any questions or come by to see it in person!",
