    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit features a factory 6-speed manual gearbox and has received critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain is anchored by a functional limited-slip differential, while the chassis has been enhanced with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed bushings for precise lateral stability. Recent compression numbers are optimal, and the cooling system has been updated with an aluminum radiator to prevent thermal fatigue. While showing minor patina indicative of its well-maintained status, this M3 is a turnkey performer for the serious driver.",
